      'Can be enriched later with impact, responsibilities, and links.',
    ],
  },
  'jumbo-vtex': {
    summaryEn:
      'Migration and full rebuild from VTEX legacy to VTEX IO for Tiendas Jumbo Colombia.',
    bulletsEn: [
      'Rebuilt the website by migrating from VTEX legacy to VTEX IO.',
      'Improved promotion workflows and dynamic content management.',
      'Componentized sections and customized checkout flows for business needs.',
      'Worked in a 3-developer team with technical leadership and VTEX IO solution design responsibilities.',
    ],
  },
  'hotel-management': {
    summaryEn:
      'Hotel management web app focused on collaborative workflows, best practices, and team delivery.',
    bulletsEn: [
      'Built a web app from scratch for hotel operations management.',
      'Developed with a 10-person team using SCRUM.',
      'Worked in rotating pairs to collaborate across the whole team.',
      'Used Git and Airtable for task organization and project tracking.',
